    • getFieldFromObject

      private java.lang.Object getFieldFromObject​(java.lang.Object object, java.lang.String fieldName)
      Helper method to get any field from any object, public or private. Any object returned by this method need to be casted to the desired type. Will print to stacktrace if the field is not found.
      Parameters:
      object - a Object reference for the object from which a Field is desired.
      fieldName - String name of the field for use by reflection
      Returns:
      a Object reference
